/p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">萨姆·芬德 (Sam Fender)</a>开玩笑说，他的新专辑现已完成并“掌握”，并得到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-war-on-drugs">The War On Drugs</a>的 Adam Granduciel 的参与。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="555" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/sam-fender-cover-interview-2021-seventeen-going-under-2988647"><b>Sam Fender 登上封面：“这张专辑可能是我一生中做过的最好的事情”</b></a></li></ul><p>本周早些时候，这位 Geordie 创作型歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-shares-teaser-of-euphoric-new-song-3799044">在他的 Instagram Stories 上分享了一首欢快新歌的预告片</a>，其中两个片段 24 小时开放。</p><p>现在，在另一篇 Instagram 帖子中，Fender 简单地写了“mastered x”，并附上了一系列有关这张唱片制作过程的照片和视频。查看下面的帖子： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DAvs3ObIP2b/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4